{"data":{"post":{"id":"63fd430c-960e-5cfb-8713-74358727c528","html":"<p>先上最后结果的渲染器：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lgltracer.com/\">lgltracer</a></p>\n<p>几个Demo和效果图：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lgltracer.com/cornellBox/index.html\">CornellBox</a></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">  \n\n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/cornellBox-4b38ad4d2b4bbfc485fb6609bcb378be-e4aee.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\" alt=\"cornellBox\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/cornellBox-4b38ad4d2b4bbfc485fb6609bcb378be-48538.png\" srcset=\"/static/cornellBox-4b38ad4d2b4bbfc485fb6609bcb378be-bed0f.png 200w,\n/static/cornellBox-4b38ad4d2b4bbfc485fb6609bcb378be-5fd34.png 400w,\n/static/cornellBox-4b38ad4d2b4bbfc485fb6609bcb378be-48538.png 800w,\n/static/cornellBox-4b38ad4d2b4bbfc485fb6609bcb378be-b70ec.png 1200w,\n/static/cornellBox-4b38ad4d2b4bbfc485fb6609bcb378be-d134a.png 1600w,\n/static/cornellBox-4b38ad4d2b4bbfc485fb6609bcb378be-f6ead.png 2400w,\n/static/cornellBox-4b38ad4d2b4bbfc485fb6609bcb378be-e4aee.png 2560w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n      \n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://lgltracer.com/viewer/index.html\">GLTF Viewer</a></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">  \n\n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/gltf1-34d19eade30220b033d2f03c95822633-e4aee.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\" alt=\"gltf1\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/gltf1-34d19eade30220b033d2f03c95822633-48538.png\" srcset=\"/static/gltf1-34d19eade30220b033d2f03c95822633-bed0f.png 200w,\n/static/gltf1-34d19eade30220b033d2f03c95822633-5fd34.png 400w,\n/static/gltf1-34d19eade30220b033d2f03c95822633-48538.png 800w,\n/static/gltf1-34d19eade30220b033d2f03c95822633-b70ec.png 1200w,\n/static/gltf1-34d19eade30220b033d2f03c95822633-d134a.png 1600w,\n/static/gltf1-34d19eade30220b033d2f03c95822633-f6ead.png 2400w,\n/static/gltf1-34d19eade30220b033d2f03c95822633-e4aee.png 2560w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n      \n</div>\n<p>DiningRoom</p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">  \n\n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/diningRoom-0d7c6660a55a36e09a032628a6185fec-e4aee.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\" alt=\"diningRoom\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/diningRoom-0d7c6660a55a36e09a032628a6185fec-48538.png\" srcset=\"/static/diningRoom-0d7c6660a55a36e09a032628a6185fec-bed0f.png 200w,\n/static/diningRoom-0d7c6660a55a36e09a032628a6185fec-5fd34.png 400w,\n/static/diningRoom-0d7c6660a55a36e09a032628a6185fec-48538.png 800w,\n/static/diningRoom-0d7c6660a55a36e09a032628a6185fec-b70ec.png 1200w,\n/static/diningRoom-0d7c6660a55a36e09a032628a6185fec-d134a.png 1600w,\n/static/diningRoom-0d7c6660a55a36e09a032628a6185fec-f6ead.png 2400w,\n/static/diningRoom-0d7c6660a55a36e09a032628a6185fec-e4aee.png 2560w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n      \n</div>\n<p>光追的效果是不是让你燃起了曲线救国锤一波Sketchfab的希望呢</p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">  \n\n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/woo-5b00462dd46fbb37a6878a8dd0a47d1b-34f26.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 720px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\" alt=\"woo\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/woo-5b00462dd46fbb37a6878a8dd0a47d1b-34f26.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/woo-5b00462dd46fbb37a6878a8dd0a47d1b-a3779.jpg 200w,\n/static/woo-5b00462dd46fbb37a6878a8dd0a47d1b-3e4a1.jpg 400w,\n/static/woo-5b00462dd46fbb37a6878a8dd0a47d1b-34f26.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n      \n</div>\n<p>本系列文章就是对自己渲染器的一个总结，包括了涉及的基础理论知识和实践落地遇到的一些问题，在此分享给有缘的兄弟，希望能有所帮助吧。下一个拯救国内Web3D的人，就是你啦！</p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">  \n\n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/you-26d61e0520a65e82163913fa841a07fb-91aa6.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 81.87435633367663%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\" alt=\"you\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/you-26d61e0520a65e82163913fa841a07fb-48538.png\" srcset=\"/static/you-26d61e0520a65e82163913fa841a07fb-bed0f.png 200w,\n/static/you-26d61e0520a65e82163913fa841a07fb-5fd34.png 400w,\n/static/you-26d61e0520a65e82163913fa841a07fb-48538.png 800w,\n/static/you-26d61e0520a65e82163913fa841a07fb-91aa6.png 971w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n      \n</div>\n<p>话不多说，颠个勺开始吧：</p>\n<p>【WebGL与光线追踪】(二) Disney BSDF</p>\n<p>【WebGL与光线追踪】(三) Path Tracing</p>\n<p>【WebGL与光线追踪】(四) 实践及工程化</p>\n<p>材质与Tracing其实都已老生常谈，这里也并没有啥新的东西，关于这两者其实已有很多前辈总结的优秀文章，若是已比较熟悉的兄弟可直接略过。最后是总结了一下实践过程遇到的一些问题。</p>","fields":{"slug":"/lgltracer-intro/","prefix":"2021-11-06"},"frontmatter":{"title":"【WebGL与光线追踪】(一) 简介","author":"todaylg","category":"小结","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/gltf1-34d19eade30220b033d2f03c95822633-160fa.png"}}}}},"authornote":{"id":"20cdfd79-00b3-57fb-a29f-bb96dcd133a8","html":"<p><strong>todaylg</strong> </p>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":""}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lgltracer-intro/","prev":{"id":"590266a6-e57f-5ae9-ba05-022c4aac398d","fields":{"slug":"/hompage/","prefix":"2020-7-01","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"个人主页开发小记","category":"小结"}},"next":{"id":"301bd9f1-c11e-5291-9864-d306e3fefad6","fields":{"slug":"/lgltracer-material/","prefix":"2021-11-07","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"【WebGL与光线追踪】(二) Disney BSDF","category":"小结"}},"source":"posts"}}